body:
@josharian I'm not able to repro your failure.  Do you mind double checking that your source tree is in a consistent state?

In particular, that error message only looks possible if only half of CL 20350 was applied to your source tree somehow: CL 20350 both [changed `obj.AJMP`'s type to `obj.As`](https://github.com/golang/go/commit/0d9258a830c585c65e7ef614588d9c9a014b6123#diff-7e5b620fd9370fa324e60dcc7c9c9077R275) *and* [changed `Gbranch`'s first parameter from `int` to `obj.As`](https://github.com/golang/go/commit/0d9258a830c585c65e7ef614588d9c9a014b6123#diff-f94f1c06c0d3c9eff2e788f1e7ec09ddR82).
